4. Software

4.1 Command line interface

4.1.1. Power mangement
power       turn {on,off} power supply
reset       reset microcontroller
laser       turn {on,off} laser

4.1.2. Positioning
a           go to absolute position
r           go to relative position
d           set axis delay
park        go to inicial position
demo        demonstration mode
gage        calibrate axes

4.1.3. Information
axes        get axes current position
read        read from distance sensor
temp        get temperature from step motors driver
fan         fan information
free        show memory information
info        general system information
ver         system version
debug       enable verbose messages
